      • removeTimeSeries

        void removeTimeSeries(List<LabelValue> labelValues)
        Removes the TimeSeries from the metric, if it is present. i.e. references to previous TimeSeries are invalid (not part of the metric).
        Parameters:
        labelValues - the list of label values.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if labelValues is null.
        Since:
        0.1.0
